snippet.title: Starhawk™ - Official Launch Trailer (Available Now)
snippet.description:
From the creators of Warhawk, Starhawk revolutionizes shooters with the new Build & Battle System. Call down buildings, weapons and vehicles to shape the battlefield and dominate your enemies. Featuring a full single player campaign, Co-op modes, and epic 32 person multiplayer battles Starhawk is a must have for all shooter fans.

Starhawk - Available May 8th

Pre-order at GameStop to get the Limited Edition at no extra cost! Get over $20 worth of bonus content at the regular price of $59.99!

http://www.starhawkthegame.com/
